{"title": "How to Send Investigation Request via email?", "body": "Follow these steps on how  to send Investigation Requests using Email on Demand:\nOpen Patient Record\nClick Clinical Tab \nClick the Letter Writer icon\n\n\nFill in all required fields then click Save\n\nOn the letter writer, Click on Letter then Select Investigations\nSelect the template you want to use.\n\nData of the recent Investigation Request created will populate on the letter template selected.\nClick File then Select Save and change the status from Draft to Final\nFor additional steps in sending Requests to patients or contacts using email on demand, please see this article. How to Send an Email to Contacts or Patient.\nWhat is Email on Demand?\nEmail FAQs\n "}